name: Design Annotations & File Template Setup
description:
Components to help you organize your design file, document your designs better, and think about design work in terms of projects and activities. 

The file includes:

1. Framework for organizing pages in Figma based on 3 design stages

2. Project and Activity Cards

3. Sticky Notes

4. Feedback Cards

5. Thumbnail

6. Audit Components

7. Default App Icons
